{"tid":1801412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭紹傑及嚴敏華將於3月往日本就「侵入建築物」罪上訴","createTime":"2019-12-28T15:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T23:17:07.000Z","uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4ceb4e3cfaecf4f95725cd48494b033a154ef86d","tid":1801412,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1499935_1_L_20191228164920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1499935_1_L_20191228164920.jpg&h=96528918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港人郭紹傑及嚴敏華去年12月在日本靖國神社抗議時被捕，今年10月被判監及緩刑後獲釋返港。為兩人辯護的日本律師一瀨敬一郎表示，日本憲法對言論自由提供保障，靖國神社是公眾地方，形容兩人被控「侵入建築物罪」是荒謬的做法。<br />\n<br />\n日本「譴責打壓12.12靖國神社抗議者支援會」在本港開記者會，發言人新孝一說，郭紹傑及嚴敏華的正當抗議遭到日本政府執法及司法部門無理打壓，被拘留長達10個月，期間不獲保釋，極不人道，因此為他們提供法律支援及舉辦集會。<br />\n<br />\n去年12月12日，郭紹傑及嚴敏華在靖國神社外，高舉「毋忘南京大屠殺」橫額，焚燒甲級戰犯東條英機的道具「神主牌」及叫口號，兩人當場被捕，後來被判監禁8個月，緩刑3年，並獲釋回港，他們表示會在明年3月提出上訴。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499935-20191228.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499935-20191228.htm&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=0c5c7fc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499935-20191228.htm&h=911163cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499935-20191228.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7f510fa2bf033d3cfe4656d70dfd1d238f8a330e","tid":1801412,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n【非標題撚】其實我哋輸到仆街 - <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1801398/page/1?post=6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1801398/page/1?post=6</a>"},{"pid":"9d59a8156c3ef60ec8f49c7f7f8a298b362d4d14","tid":1801412,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:20:46.000Z","msg":"如果上訴結果